n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=5feec095\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&h=72f77df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">除咗九月八日，如果<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">十月一日</span>我地再幫支共賀一賀佢，搞到全美國都知支共國慶我地用美國國歌慶祝，你話會激到維尼幾咁高興？<br />\n<br />\n而最重要，我地之前揮動美國國旗、唱美國國歌，美國傳媒一直都理解成我地係以追求人權民主自由既普世價值而表態！！！亦係動之以情地令佢地推動 香港民主及人權法案 既方法！！！<br />\n</span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n九月八日發夢同我一齊唱！<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">MV with Lyrics: </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvPKp29Luryc&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=4775aca8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">歌詞：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nSVsMz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"ht